description: This file contains a summary of service utilization by ASC supplier and is derived from 2011 ASC line item level data, updated through June 2012, that is, line items for services furnished on or after January 1, 2011 through December 31, 2011 that were received, processed, paid, and passed to the National Claims History file by June 30, 2012. This file contains data for ASC services billed in 2011, including services that were added under the revised ASC payment system.
title: Ambulatory Surgical Center (ASC) Payment System
